{"tid":1626810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10月1號被捕義士有嘢講","createTime":"2019-10-05T13:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T16:34:35.000Z","uid":40443,"like":115,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"a4477625faa3e06f64312e1ab4487308f2b027dc","tid":1626810,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:04:35.000Z","msg":"代朋友post<br />\n我係10月1號屯門被捕義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望前線可以接受我嘅意見<br />\n我被捕時受傷，頭部流血，要求警方帶我去醫院<br />\n當時屯門玩緊鏹水，聽到佢哋講，亦親眼見到<br />\n救護車車走咗一啲受傷嘅警員去屯門醫院同天水圍醫院<br />\n我亦上咗一㗎去屯門醫院嘅救護車<br />\n但我見到嘅情況係，屯門當時開緊戰<br />\n親眼見住警方施放四粒催淚彈，去比救護車離開。我自己覺得，救護車已經唔可信，<br />\n希望前線人員如果可以截停到救護車，<br />\n麻煩截停佢睇清楚入面係，被捕嘅義士，定係一班狗<br />\n你哋可以做到嘅係救翻一班被捕嘅人士，或者拉啲落車打<br />\n我相信救護人員都係被警察利用，無需要傷害佢哋<br />\n但係如果截停到救護車嘅話，你哋可以救到義士，救得一個得一個<br />\n我唔係想分化救護人員對我哋嘅幫助<br />\n但係截停佢哋睇一睇，冇壞！<br />\n希望大家可以幫手宣傳出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea646d70c284b4be164d39b7ed9f95a3b3324bd","tid":1626810,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a422f14de36d4b547b8380347febf0dc8cabc189","tid":1626810,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0eeb9ee8662f8ff4159af1b05168db3724e7654","tid":1626810,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:06:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3160fdaa280b2dd0071e661ab06ad35491e378d","tid":1626810,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:06:28.000Z","msg":"冇人嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}